## these are the excution steps, 
- build the image
- run a container based of that image and expose it through a port
- check running containers
- access the web app via exposed port
- stop container
- remove container

## steps

1) docker build . #note we did not add a tag
2) docker run -p 3000:80 "paste image ID "
3) docker ps #check running containers
4) localhost:3000 #on your browser to check if the web app is working
5) docker stop #this will stop the container
6) docker rm "paste container name or container ID from docker ps " 

